data.description: Welcome to 13807 Hallfield, beautiful one-story 3BD 2BA Pulte home with large patio, granite countertops, and a two-car garage. Featuring high ceilings, a gas log fireplace, ceramic tile in the entry, kitchen, baths and laundry room this home. The primary bathroom has a garden tub, full length mirrors and double sinks.
